    <h2 id="page_title"><a href="http://NothingButSnark.svbtle.com">Brett Cannon</a></h2>
    <h3 id="page_subtitle"><a href="http://NothingButSnark.svbtle.com">Python core developer. Tall, snarky Canadian.</a></h3>
